The intention of this article is to provide a walk through tutorial of
the Nix expression language and helpful tips and advice for writing and
debugging Nix expressions. The canonical resources for documentation is
the [Nix Users
Manual](http://hydra.nixos.org/job/nix/trunk/tarball/latest/download-by-type/doc/manual%7C).

